{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":797,"text":"So, a few years ago I was at JFK Airport"},{"time":3578,"text":"about to get on a flight,"},{"time":5370,"text":"when I was approached by two women"},{"time":7186,"text":"who I do not think would be insulted"},{"time":8848,"text":"to hear themselves described"},{"time":10242,"text":"as tiny old tough-talking Italian-American broads."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14184,"text":"The taller one, who is like up here,"},{"time":17330,"text":"she comes marching up to me, and she goes,"},{"time":19381,"text":"\"Honey, I gotta ask you something."},{"time":21700,"text":"You got something to do with that whole"},{"time":23128,"text":"'Eat, Pray, Love' thing that's been going on lately?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":26150,"text":"And I said, \"Yes, I did.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":28264,"text":"And she smacks her friend and she goes,"},{"time":30052,"text":"\"See, I told you, I said, that's that girl."},{"time":32206,"text":"That's that girl who wrote that book"},{"time":34156,"text":"based on that movie.\""},{"time":36190,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38344,"text":"So that's who I am."},{"time":40520,"text":"And believe me, I'm extremely\ngrateful to be that person,"},{"time":44225,"text":"because that whole \"Eat, Pray, Love\" thing"},{"time":46223,"text":"was a huge break for me."},{"time":47967,"text":"But it also left me in a really tricky position"},{"time":50475,"text":"moving forward as an author"},{"time":52383,"text":"trying to figure out how in the world"},{"time":54110,"text":"I was ever going to write a book again"},{"time":55364,"text":"that would ever please anybody,"},{"time":57209,"text":"because I knew well in advance"},{"time":59199,"text":"that all of those people who\nhad adored \"Eat, Pray, Love\""},{"time":62151,"text":"were going to be incredibly disappointed"},{"time":63740,"text":"in whatever I wrote next"},{"time":65123,"text":"because it wasn't going to be \"Eat, Pray, Love,\""},{"time":66951,"text":"and all of those people who\nhad hated \"Eat, Pray, Love\""},{"time":69397,"text":"were going to be incredibly disappointed"},{"time":70765,"text":"in whatever I wrote next"},{"time":72208,"text":"because it would provide evidence that I still lived."},{"time":74661,"text":"So I knew that I had no way to win,"},{"time":77823,"text":"and knowing that I had no way to win"},{"time":80279,"text":"made me seriously consider for a while"},{"time":82183,"text":"just quitting the game"},{"time":83625,"text":"and moving to the country to raise corgis."},{"time":87267,"text":"But if I had done that, if I had given up writing,"},{"time":89327,"text":"I would have lost my beloved vocation,"},{"time":91391,"text":"so I knew that the task was that I had to find"},{"time":93599,"text":"some way to gin up the inspiration"},{"time":95998,"text":"to write the next book"},{"time":97430,"text":"regardless of its inevitable negative outcome."},{"time":99926,"text":"In other words, I had to find a way to make sure"},{"time":101534,"text":"that my creativity survived its own success."},{"time":104177,"text":"And I did, in the end, find that inspiration,"},{"time":106600,"text":"but I found it in the most unlikely"},{"time":108138,"text":"and unexpected place."},{"time":109552,"text":"I found it in lessons that I had learned earlier in life"},{"time":112692,"text":"about how creativity can survive its own failure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115800,"text":"So just to back up and explain,"},{"time":117406,"text":"the only thing I have ever wanted to be"},{"time":119719,"text":"for my whole life was a writer."},{"time":121316,"text":"I wrote all through childhood,\nall through adolescence,"},{"time":123688,"text":"by the time I was a teenager I was sending"},{"time":125504,"text":"my very bad stories to The New Yorker,"},{"time":127340,"text":"hoping to be discovered."},{"time":128616,"text":"After college, I got a job as a diner waitress,"},{"time":131060,"text":"kept working, kept writing,"},{"time":133196,"text":"kept trying really hard to get published,"},{"time":135444,"text":"and failing at it."},{"time":137156,"text":"I failed at getting published"},{"time":138628,"text":"for almost six years."},{"time":140204,"text":"So for almost six years, every single day,"},{"time":141812,"text":"I had nothing but rejection letters"},{"time":143468,"text":"waiting for me in my mailbox."},{"time":145120,"text":"And it was devastating every single time,"},{"time":146870,"text":"and every single time, I had to ask myself"},{"time":149114,"text":"if I should just quit while I was behind"},{"time":151500,"text":"and give up and spare myself this pain."},{"time":155190,"text":"But then I would find my resolve,"},{"time":156484,"text":"and always in the same way,"},{"time":158006,"text":"by saying, \"I'm not going to quit,"},{"time":160151,"text":"I'm going home.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":161972,"text":"And you have to understand that for me,"},{"time":162920,"text":"going home did not mean\nreturning to my family's farm."},{"time":166492,"text":"For me, going home"},{"time":168050,"text":"meant returning to the work of writing"},{"time":169601,"text":"because writing was my home,"},{"time":171486,"text":"because I loved writing more\nthan I hated failing at writing,"},{"time":174702,"text":"which is to say that I loved writing"},{"time":176207,"text":"more than I loved my own ego,"},{"time":177780,"text":"which is ultimately to say"},{"time":179184,"text":"that I loved writing more than I loved myself."},{"time":181776,"text":"And that's how I pushed through it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":183742,"text":"But the weird thing is that 20 years later,"},{"time":185606,"text":"during the crazy ride of \"Eat, Pray, Love,\""},{"time":187104,"text":"I found myself identifying all over again"},{"time":189710,"text":"with that unpublished young diner waitress"},{"time":192110,"text":"who I used to be, thinking about her constantly,"},{"time":194278,"text":"and feeling like I was her again,"},{"time":196136,"text":"which made no rational sense whatsoever"},{"time":197901,"text":"because our lives could not\nhave been more different."},{"time":199878,"text":"She had failed constantly."},{"time":201326,"text":"I had succeeded beyond my wildest expectation."},{"time":203970,"text":"We had nothing in common."},{"time":205320,"text":"Why did I suddenly feel like I was her all over again?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":208486,"text":"And it was only when I was trying to unthread that"},{"time":210856,"text":"that I finally began to comprehend"},{"time":212458,"text":"the strange and unlikely psychological connection"},{"time":214862,"text":"in our lives between the way\nwe experience great failure"},{"time":217396,"text":"and the way we experience great success."},{"time":219632,"text":"So think of it like this:"},{"time":221102,"text":"For most of your life, you live out your existence"},{"time":222852,"text":"here in the middle of the chain of human experience"},{"time":225295,"text":"where everything is normal\nand reassuring and regular,"},{"time":228373,"text":"but failure catapults you abruptly way out over here"},{"time":231833,"text":"into the blinding darkness of disappointment."},{"time":234767,"text":"Success catapults you just as abruptly but just as far"},{"time":238321,"text":"way out over here"},{"time":239689,"text":"into the equally blinding glare"},{"time":241551,"text":"of fame and recognition and praise."},{"time":244403,"text":"And one of these fates"},{"time":245605,"text":"is objectively seen by the world as bad,"},{"time":247822,"text":"and the other one is objectively\nseen by the world as good,"},{"time":249879,"text":"but your subconscious is completely incapable"},{"time":252527,"text":"of discerning the difference between bad and good."},{"time":255255,"text":"The only thing that it is capable of feeling"},{"time":257396,"text":"is the absolute value of this emotional equation,"},{"time":260856,"text":"the exact distance that you have been flung"},{"time":263471,"text":"from yourself."},{"time":264839,"text":"And there's a real equal danger in both cases"},{"time":266895,"text":"of getting lost out there"},{"time":268441,"text":"in the hinterlands of the psyche."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270465,"text":"But in both cases, it turns out that there is"},{"time":271998,"text":"also the same remedy for self-restoration,"},{"time":274822,"text":"and that is that you have got to\nfind your way back home again"},{"time":278420,"text":"as swiftly and smoothly as you can,"},{"time":280687,"text":"and if you're wondering what your home is,"},{"time":282159,"text":"here's a hint:"},{"time":283245,"text":"Your home is whatever in this world you love"},{"time":285471,"text":"more than you love yourself."},{"time":287385,"text":"So that might be creativity, it might be family,"},{"time":289471,"text":"it might be invention, adventure,"},{"time":291447,"text":"faith, service, it might be raising corgis,"},{"time":294239,"text":"I don't know, your home is that thing"},{"time":296139,"text":"to which you can dedicate your energies"},{"time":297911,"text":"with such singular devotion"},{"time":299957,"text":"that the ultimate results become inconsequential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303359,"text":"For me, that home has always been writing."},{"time":305863,"text":"So after the weird, disorienting success"},{"time":308435,"text":"that I went through with \"Eat, Pray, Love,\""},{"time":310133,"text":"I realized that all I had to do was exactly"},{"time":311547,"text":"the same thing that I used to have to do all the time"},{"time":313531,"text":"when I was an equally disoriented failure."},{"time":315761,"text":"I had to get my ass back to work,"},{"time":317539,"text":"and that's what I did, and that's how, in 2010,"},{"time":320047,"text":"I was able to publish the dreaded follow-up"},{"time":322401,"text":"to \"Eat, Pray, Love.\""},{"time":323289,"text":"And you know what happened with that book?"},{"time":324865,"text":"It bombed, and I was fine."},{"time":327576,"text":"Actually, I kind of felt bulletproof,"},{"time":329425,"text":"because I knew that I had broken the spell"},{"time":331545,"text":"and I had found my way back home"},{"time":333190,"text":"to writing for the sheer devotion of it."},{"time":335801,"text":"And I stayed in my home of writing after that,"},{"time":337937,"text":"and I wrote another book that just came out last year"},{"time":339769,"text":"and that one was really beautifully received,"},{"time":341414,"text":"which is very nice, but not my point."},{"time":342910,"text":"My point is that I'm writing another one now,"},{"time":345200,"text":"and I'll write another book after that"},{"time":346387,"text":"and another and another and another"},{"time":348217,"text":"and many of them will fail,"},{"time":349415,"text":"and some of them might succeed,"},{"time":351043,"text":"but I will always be safe"},{"time":352639,"text":"from the random hurricanes of outcome"},{"time":355011,"text":"as long as I never forget where I rightfully live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":358561,"text":"Look, I don't know where you rightfully live,"},{"time":360963,"text":"but I know that there's something in this world"},{"time":362633,"text":"that you love more than you love yourself."},{"time":364705,"text":"Something worthy, by the way,"},{"time":366120,"text":"so addiction and infatuation don't count,"},{"time":368111,"text":"because we all know that those\nare not safe places to live. Right?"},{"time":372218,"text":"The only trick is that you've got to identify"},{"time":374265,"text":"the best, worthiest thing that you love most,"},{"time":376729,"text":"and then build your house right on top of it"},{"time":379100,"text":"and don't budge from it."},{"time":380977,"text":"And if you should someday, somehow"},{"time":383321,"text":"get vaulted out of your home"},{"time":385265,"text":"by either great failure or great success,"},{"time":387705,"text":"then your job is to fight your\nway back to that home"},{"time":389870,"text":"the only way that it has ever been done,"},{"time":391655,"text":"by putting your head down and performing"},{"time":393844,"text":"with diligence and devotion"},{"time":395666,"text":"and respect and reverence"},{"time":397352,"text":"whatever the task is that love"},{"time":399396,"text":"is calling forth from you next."},{"time":401476,"text":"You just do that, and keep doing that"},{"time":403660,"text":"again and again and again,"},{"time":405309,"text":"and I can absolutely promise you,\nfrom long personal experience"},{"time":407965,"text":"in every direction, I can assure you"},{"time":410220,"text":"that it's all going to be okay."},{"time":412290,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":413981,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}